display_long_description:
EARLY SUPPORTER BUILD – NOT FOR GENERAL PURCHASE
This page exists so users can follow the project and add it to their wishlist

Follow progress on Discord - https://discord.gg/QfmQMzz2ep

Under Development! Early Prototype:
This is a supporter-only build intended for early backers and game testers. The price is intentionally set high to avoid general purchases. This version is not ready for public play and does not represent the final game

This game is a solo-developed project. Every line of code, all gameplay systems, city environments, vehicles, and AI have been built by a single person with a simple goal: to push the limits of what’s possible on mobile VR and deliver a large-scale open-world experience

Because of this, development takes time, and support from early followers truly makes a difference

A normal release price will be set later once the project reaches a stable public build.
If you choose to support this project, your purchase directly funds development, art, performance optimization, and future content creation

Early access!  ADD TO WISHLIST to be notified when the final release becomes available
